This paper deals with facial image analysis and generation using deep learning techniques, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves age estimation and personalized identity preservation, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the paper uses image manipulation techniques, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
